# Add New API Route

Create a new Next.js Route Handler for the `{{routeName}}` resource following this pattern:

1. Create `src/app/api/{{routeName}}/route.ts` with GET and POST handlers
2. Create `src/app/api/{{routeName}}/[id]/route.ts` with GET, PUT, DELETE handlers
3. Add corresponding functions to `src/lib/api.ts`
4. Use proper HTTP status codes and error handling
5. Follow the TypeScript types in `src/lib/types.ts`